#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid "card reader"
msgstr "讀卡器"

#. ~ Description for card reader
#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"This is a smartcard reader.  It sports the stylized symbol of an atom inside"
" a flask that is universally known to indicate SCIENCE.  The stark red LED "
"blinks askance at your geek cred.  You could swipe a scientific ID badge "
"near it to unlock the gates to discovery."
msgstr ""
"這是一臺智能卡讀卡器。它展示著一個燒瓶內原子風格化的符號，這是普遍代表科學的標誌。醒目的紅色LED燈閃爍著，彷彿在質疑你的極客資歷。你可以用科學ID徽章在附近刷卡，以解鎖通往發現的大門。"

#. ~ Description for card reader
#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"This is a smartcard reader.  The universal symbol of an eagle driving a "
"tank, biting a grenade pin stands rampant in front of an American flag.  A "
"small, red LED remains constant, as if watching you, waiting.  You could "
"swipe a military ID card in front of the reader if you dared."
msgstr ""
"這是一臺智能卡讀卡器。一隻鷹駕駛坦克、咬著手榴彈插銷的通用符號，在美國國旗前傲然挺立。一個小小的紅色LED燈持續亮著，彷彿在監視你、等待著你。如果你敢的話，可以在讀卡器前刷一張軍事ID卡。"

#. ~ Description for card reader
#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"This is a smartcard reader.  The symbol of a gear in front of a bulging "
"bicep is emblazoned on the matte black surface with an illegible heavy "
"industrial company title.  A red LED blinks on the card reader.  Perhaps an "
"industrial ID card could still open it."
msgstr ""
"這是一臺智能卡讀卡器。一個齒輪前凸起二頭肌的符號，印在啞光黑色表面上，旁邊是難以辨認的重工業公司名稱。讀卡器上的紅色LED燈閃爍。或許一張工業ID卡仍能打開它。"

#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Gud lava"
msgstr "古德熔岩"

#. ~ Description for Gud lava
#: .\Furniture-Terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"An extremely hot, glowing liquid, composed of molten rock and/or metal.Not "
"deadly at all compared to vanilla so Kevin will truly despise this"
msgstr "一種極其熾熱、發光的液體，由熔化的岩石和/或金屬組成。與原版相比完全不致命，所以凱文肯定會鄙視這個。"

#: .\Items\ammo.json .\Items\ammo_types.json
msgid "BL9 Sample"
msgid_plural "BL9 Samples"
msgstr[0] "BL9樣本"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Sample', 'str_pl': 'BL9 Samples'}
#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An organism sample of a very strange and unknown origin, as you touch it you"
" can clearly feel how it's vibrating, moving, as if it's particles are "
"constantly communicating with each other"
msgstr "一種來源非常奇特未知的生物樣本，當你觸摸它時，可以清晰地感覺到它在振動、移動，彷彿它的粒子在不斷相互交流"

#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid "BL9 Sample MK ii"
msgid_plural "BL9 Samples MK ii"
msgstr[0] "BL9樣本MK ii"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Sample MK ii', 'str_pl': 'BL9 Samples MK
#. ii'}
#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An organism sample of a very strange and unknown origin, as you touch it you"
" can clearly see how it's changing it's color, shifting from one unknown "
"state of matter to another as if modified by an alien technology"
msgstr "一種來源非常奇特未知的生物樣本，當你觸摸它時，可以清晰地看到它如何改變顏色，從一種未知的物質狀態轉換到另一種，彷彿被外星技術改造過"

#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid "BL9 Sample MK iii"
msgid_plural "BL9 Samples MK iii"
msgstr[0] "BL9樣本MK iii"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Sample MK iii', 'str_pl': 'BL9 Samples MK
#. iii'}
#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An organism sample of a very strange and unknown origin, as you touch it you"
" can clearly feel how it's vibrating, moving, it's particles are constantly "
"reshaping and shifting, as if commanding each other"
msgstr "一種來源非常奇特未知的生物樣本，當你觸摸它時，可以清晰地感覺到它在振動、移動，它的粒子在不斷重塑和變換，彷彿在相互指揮"

#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid "BL9 Sample MK iv"
msgid_plural "BL9 Samples MK iv"
msgstr[0] "BL9樣本MK iv型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Sample MK iv', 'str_pl': 'BL9 Samples MK
#. iv'}
#: .\Items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An organism sample of a very strange and unknown origin, as you touch it you"
" can clearly see how it's swiftly changing it's colors, emitting vibrant "
"rays of light, changing from one unknown state of matter to another, as if "
"it was created by an alien technology"
msgstr ""
"一種來源極其奇特未知的生物樣本，當你觸摸它時，可以清晰地看到它迅速變換色彩，散發出鮮豔的光芒，從一種未知的物質狀態轉變為另一種，彷彿是由外星科技創造而成。"

