#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 ammo pouch"
msgid_plural "BL9 ammo pouches"
msgstr[0] "BL9 彈藥袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 ammo pouch', 'str_pl': 'BL9 ammo pouches'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A small BL9 pouch that can be used to store most types of small, medium size"
" ammunition including most of BL9 ammunition, rockets, however, will not "
"fit.  Activate to store ammunition."
msgstr "一個小型 BL9 袋，可用於存儲大多數類型的小型、中型彈藥，包括大部分 BL9 彈藥，但火箭彈無法放入。激活以存儲彈藥。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 quiver"
msgid_plural "BL9 quivers"
msgstr[0] "BL9 箭袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 quiver'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A BL9 quiver worn at the waist that can hold 20 arrows or bolts including "
"BL9 versions of them.  Activate to store arrows or bolts."
msgstr "一個系在腰間的 BL9 箭袋，可容納 20 支箭或弩箭，包括它們的 BL9 版本。激活以存儲箭或弩箭。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 large quiver"
msgid_plural "BL9 large quivers"
msgstr[0] "BL9 大型箭袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 large quiver'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A large BL9 quiver trimmed with metal, worn on the back, that can hold 60 "
"arrows or bolts including BL9 versions of them.  Historically used by horse "
"archers, rather than foot archers, but neither of THEM had to fight zombies."
"  Activate to store arrows or bolts."
msgstr ""
"一個大型、金屬鑲邊的 BL9 箭袋，背在背上，可容納 60 支箭或弩箭，包括它們的 BL9 "
"版本。歷史上由騎射手而非步射手使用，但他們都不必與殭屍戰鬥。激活以存儲箭或弩箭。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 leg ammo pouch"
msgid_plural "BL9 leg ammo pouches"
msgstr[0] "BL9腿部彈藥袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 leg ammo pouch', 'str_pl': 'BL9 leg ammo
#. pouches'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A small BL9 pouch wrapped around the leg that can be used to store most "
"types of small, medium size ammunition including most of BL9 ammunition, "
"rockets, however, will not fit.  Activate to store ammunition."
msgstr "一個系在腿上的小型BL9袋，可用於存放大多數類型的小型、中型彈藥，包括大部分BL9彈藥，但火箭彈無法放入。激活以存放彈藥。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 experimental survivor helmet"
msgid_plural "BL9 experimental survivor helmets"
msgstr[0] "BL9實驗型倖存者頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 experimental survivor helmet'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A highly experimental sleek and futuristic survivor helmet with a unique "
"design that is infused with physically and chemically structure-wise "
"modified BL9 to be versatile, enhance the user's capabilities "
"(<color_light_blue>+2 int, +2 per</color>) and offer better environmental "
"protection"
msgstr ""
"一款高度實驗性、流線型且未來感的倖存者頭盔，採用獨特設計，融合了物理和化學結構改良的BL9材料，具備多功能性，能增強使用者能力（<color_light_blue>+2智力，+2感知</color>）並提供更好的環境防護。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 experimental survivor cargo pants"
msgid_plural "BL9 experimental survivor cargo pantss"
msgstr[0] "BL9實驗型倖存者工裝褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 experimental survivor cargo pants'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"Highly experimental sleek and futuristic pair of survivor cargo pants with a"
" unique design that is infused with physically and chemically structure-wise"
" modified BL9 to be versatile, enhance the user's capabilities "
"(<color_light_blue>+1 str, +2 dex</color>) and offer better environmental "
"protection"
msgstr ""
"一款高度實驗性、流線型且未來感的倖存者工裝褲，採用獨特設計，融合了物理和化學結構改良的BL9材料，具備多功能性，能增強使用者能力（<color_light_blue>+1力量，+2敏捷</color>）並提供更好的環境防護。"

#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid "BL9 experimental survivor suit"
msgid_plural "BL9 experimental survivor suits"
msgstr[0] "BL9實驗型倖存者套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 experimental survivor suit'}
#: .\Items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A highly experimental sleek and futuristic survivor suit with a unique "
"design that is infused with physically and chemically structure-wise "
"modified BL9 to be versatile, enhance the user's capabilities "
"(<color_light_blue>+1 str, +1 dex, +1 int, +1 per, -10% to attack cost, +10%"
" to action points</color>) and offer better environmental protection"
