#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid "BL9 Shield Generator"
msgid_plural "BL9 Shield Generators"
msgstr[0] "BL9護盾發生器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Shield Generator'}
#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid ""
"Incredible technologically advanced relatively small device which is capable"
" of generating an energy shield around itself of a massive size. Currently "
"turned off with only way of turning it on known to exile Davranide scientist"
" that you are likely to be acquainted with already from journals which you "
"can read. Exile Davranide scientist has programmed BL9 Safety Bases Android "
"system to be able to turn shield generator on because he himself has created"
" this shield generator"
msgstr ""
"技術先進的非凡小型裝置，能生成覆蓋巨大範圍的能量護盾。目前處於關閉狀態，唯一啟動方式由流亡達夫拉尼德科學家掌握（你可能已從日誌中瞭解此人），該科學家因創造此護盾發生器而將啟動權限編程至BL9安全基地安卓系統"

#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid "BL9 Hidden Safety Bases Map"
msgid_plural "BL9 Hidden Safety Bases Maps"
msgstr[0] "BL9隱藏安全基地地圖"

#. ~ Use action message for {'str': 'BL9 Hidden Safety Bases Map'}.
#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid ""
"You carefully examine the map and spot the entrances of BL9 Safety Bases "
"hopefully"
msgstr "你仔細檢查地圖，滿懷希望地發現了BL9安全基地的入口。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Hidden Safety Bases Map'}
#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid ""
"Long-time survivors, we are in need of your help. This map contains "
"locations of BL9 Safety Bases, where you should to go to receive further "
"instructions. All explanations will be provided to you by Strange Merchant "
"along with our Base Androids that can find locations, via it's hi-tech "
"locating system, that are crucial for acquiring gear which can play a key "
"role in fending off these invaders that are terrorizing us so if you want to"
" help us, go to one of BL9 Safety Bases, where you should to talk to Strange"
" Merchant along with one of our Base Androids to receive further "
"instructions"
msgstr ""
"久經考驗的倖存者們，我們需要你們的幫助。這張地圖標註了BL9安全基地的位置，你們應前往那裡獲取進一步指示。所有說明將由神秘商人以及我們的基地安卓機器人提供，它們能通過高科技定位系統找到關鍵地點，這些地點對於獲取裝備至關重要，這些裝備在抵禦那些恐嚇我們的入侵者時能發揮關鍵作用。因此，若你們願意幫助我們，請前往任意一個BL9安全基地，在那裡與神秘商人及我們的一名基地安卓機器人交談以接收進一步指示。"

#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid "BL9 Hidden Structures Of Hostile Tyrants Along With Aliens Map"
msgid_plural "BL9 Hidden Structures Of Hostile Tyrants Along With Aliens Maps"
msgstr[0] "BL9敵對暴君與外星人隱藏結構地圖"

#. ~ Use action message for {'str': 'BL9 Hidden Structures Of Hostile Tyrants
#. Along With Aliens Map'}.
#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid ""
"You carefully examine the map and spot the entrances of structures of "
"various hostile forces hopefully"
msgstr "你仔細檢查地圖，滿懷希望地發現了各種敵對勢力結構的入口。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Hidden Structures Of Hostile Tyrants Along
#. With Aliens Map'}
#: .\Items\generic.json
msgid ""
"This map contains locations of hostile forces that hunt for BL9 to weaponize"
" it for their conquests. If you are not sure about your gear, here is "
"advised order of locations based on their difficulty. Castlelan Castle, "
"Infested Facility, Militarized Island, Guard Towers with Hive Caves, "
"Underground Ruins, Acidic Caves, Sunken Caves, Molten Caves, Mobile Alliance"
" Base in this order, which is advised only if you are not sure about your "
"gear hopefully. These structures contain a lot of rare gear that even "
"Strange Merchant does not sell along with materials to craft BL9 ammo"
msgstr ""
"這張地圖標註了那些為將BL9武器化以用於征服而追獵它的敵對勢力的位置。如果你對自己的裝備沒有把握，以下是基於難度建議的地點順序：卡斯特蘭城堡、感染設施、軍事化島嶼、帶蜂巢洞穴的守衛塔、地下廢墟、酸性洞穴、沉沒洞穴、熔岩洞穴、移動聯盟基地，此順序僅在你對自身裝備不確定時建議遵循。這些結構中藏有大量稀有裝備，甚至連神秘商人都不會出售，同時還有用於製作BL9彈藥的素材。"

