msgid_plural "BL9 enhanced acid-resistant tanks"
msgstr[0] "BL9增強型耐酸罐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 enhanced acid-resistant tank'}
#: .\Items\magazines.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift 2L canister containing an even more corrosive living liquified "
"BL9 that has very strong acidic properties, may be used in a makeshift `BL9 "
"sprayer`"
msgstr "一個臨時製作的2升罐子，內含更具腐蝕性的活體液化BL9，具有極強的酸性，可用於臨時製作的`BL9噴霧器`"

#: .\Items\magazines.json
msgid "BL9 enhanced heat-resistant tank"
msgid_plural "BL9 enhanced heat-resistant tanks"
