#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 super heat-resistant tank'}
#: .\Items\magazines.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift 2L canister containing a living liquified BL9 that is in a pure "
"magmatic state capable of melting anything or so it seems, may be used in a "
"makeshift `BL9 melting sprayer`"
msgstr "一個臨時製作的2升罐子，內含活體液化BL9，處於純岩漿狀態，似乎能熔化一切，可用於臨時製作的`BL9熔化噴霧器`"

