"A highly experimental futuristic whip with a unique design that uses BL9 "
"capable of changing it's physical and chemical structure to cause various "
"offensive effects, in this case, extremely corrosive stream of BL9"
msgstr "一把高度實驗性的未來主義鞭，採用獨特設計，使用能夠改變其物理和化學結構的BL9來產生多種攻擊效果，在此情況下為BL9的強腐蝕性流束。"

