#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Herb Cleansing"
msgstr "草藥淨化"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Herb Cleansing'.
#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid ""
"You have taken some healing herb.  It appears to have panacea-like effects "
"along with radiation cleansing properties slowly cleansing your body of "
"radiation; if you take more of it, you'll be able to speed up the process."
msgstr "你服用了一些治療草藥。它似乎具有類似萬靈藥的效果，同時具備輻射淨化特性，正緩慢清除你體內的輻射；若服用更多，將能加速此過程。"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Mild Herb Stun"
msgstr "輕度草藥眩暈"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
