msgstr "強力草藥眩暈"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Intense Herb Stun"
msgstr "劇烈草藥眩暈"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid ""
"You have taken some healing herb.  It appears to have pretty strong "
"stunning, dizzying effects; these effects are temporary, but if you take "
"more of it right away, they will stack."
msgstr "你服用了一些治療草藥。它似乎具有相當強烈的眩暈和致暈效果；這些效果是暫時的，但如果你立即服用更多，它們會疊加。"

