msgstr "BL9 高級健康"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Advanced Healthiness'}
#: .\Monsters\mon_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You feel an incredible boost in health (+55% to health) while wearing this "
"particular artifact, it feels not as if you're controlled but guided by an "
"entity or so you think..."
