#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"No dejes que se escape!\""
msgstr "\"別讓他跑了！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Te voy a romper en pedazos!\""
msgstr "\"我要把你撕成碎片！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"A trespasser! Kill, kill, KILL!\""
msgstr "\"入侵者！殺，殺，殺！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"You shall NOT defile our holy sanctuaries, filthy outsider!\""
msgstr "\"你休想玷汙我們的神聖聖所，骯髒的外來者！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"It's all coming together! The prophecy, Nevulion, we will feast on your "
"blood!\""
msgstr "\"一切都在匯聚！預言，內瓦里恩，我們將暢飲你的鮮血！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"I have tasted the blood of fallen angels!\""
msgstr "\"我已品嚐過墮落天使之血！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"I have seen beyond the world of skin, the architecture of blood and bone "
"marrow!\""
msgstr "\"我已窺見皮膚世界之外的景象，那鮮血與骨髓構築的架構！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Matalo!\""
msgstr "\"殺了他！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Alli esta!\""
msgstr "\"他在那兒！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Cogedlo, cogedlo, cogedlo...\""
msgstr "\"抓住他，抓住他，抓住他……\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"This is harder than kidnapping a president's daughter!\""
msgstr "\"這比綁架總統女兒還難！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Ugh, I remember when I didn't have to cook to eat human meat in our "
"Castle, not to mention hunt for it!\""
msgstr "\"呃，我還記得在我們城堡裡不用烹飪就能吃到人肉的日子，更別提還要親自狩獵了！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"So, first, we had that treacherous scum of a scientist, then fucking "
"mister special agent, then fucking snake in a red dress, then others, now "
"you! We are just trying to spread Nevulion's blessings!\""
msgstr "\"先是那個背信棄義的科學家渣滓，然後是那個該死的特工先生，接著是那個穿紅裙子的婊子蛇，還有其他人，現在又是你！我們只是想傳播內瓦里恩的祝福！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Cerebros, cerebros, cerebros...\""
msgstr "\"大腦，大腦，大腦……\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Intruder!\""
msgstr "\"闖入者！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Each step you make only brings you closer to getting torn apart, "
"trespasser!\""
msgstr "\"你每走一步，都離被撕碎更近一步，入侵者！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"There you are!\""
msgstr "\"找到你了！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"No point in hiding, I will find you sooner or later and tear your heart "
"out!\""
msgstr "\"躲藏毫無意義，我遲早會找到你，掏出你的心臟！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"You are nothing!\""
msgstr "\"你什麼都不是！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"I will end you HERE!\""
msgstr "\"我要在這裡終結你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"I shall tear to pieces what remains of you to my heart's content!\""
msgstr "\"我要隨心所欲地將你剩餘的軀體撕成碎片！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"My Master will be happy to see your barely recognizable severed head!\""
msgstr "\"我的主人會很高興看到你那幾乎無法辨認的斷頭！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Pathetic little brat, I am one of the right hands of my Master!\""
msgstr "\"可悲的小鬼，我可是主人的得力助手之一！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You're a strong warrior, Nevulion would have bestowed a blessing upon you "
"had you not been such a stubborn resistant brat!\""
msgstr "\"你是個強大的戰士，若不是如此頑固抵抗，內瓦里恩本會賜福於你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Hehehe, that tickles!\""
msgstr "\"嘿嘿嘿，撓癢癢呢！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Hahaha, that tickles!\""
msgstr "\"哈哈哈，撓癢癢呢！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Such animal strength and relentlessness - you'll be a great sacrifice for "
"Nevulion!\""
msgstr "\"如此野獸般的力量與不屈——你將成為獻給內瓦里恩的絕佳祭品！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"The prophecy IS already happening and your feeble attempts to stop it "
"merely postpone the inevitable, Nevulion has already entered our realm!\""
msgstr "\"預言正在實現，你那些阻止它的微弱嘗試只是推遲了必然之事，內瓦里恩已降臨我們的領域！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Nevulion's blood flows through my veins!\""
msgstr "\"內瓦里恩之血在我血管中流淌！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"This WILL be completed with a human sacrifice - and that is YOU!\""
msgstr "\"這將以一場人祭完成——而祭品就是你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Intruder! I need backup, NOW!\""
msgstr "\"入侵者！我需要支援，立刻！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Secure the perimeter! Eliminate the target, NOW!\""
msgstr "\"封鎖周邊！消滅目標，立刻！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Hostile in the area!\""
msgstr "\"區域內有敵對分子！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Security breach, REPEAT, security breach!\""
msgstr "\"安全漏洞，重複，安全漏洞！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"You will not escape alive!\""
msgstr "\"你休想活著逃脫！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"You are up against an unbeatable force, scum!\""
msgstr "\"你面對的是不可戰勝的力量，渣滓！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Rebel scum!\""
msgstr "\"叛軍渣滓！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"'Unstoppable'? We are better trained, better equipped, and superior to "
"this scum in every way that counts! ELIMINATE THE TARGET, NOW!\""
msgstr "\"‘不可阻擋’？我們訓練更精良，裝備更先進，在各方面都遠超這些渣滓！消滅目標，立刻！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Just like the simulations!\""
msgstr "\"就像模擬訓練一樣！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You underestimate the power of the...just kidding! ELIMINATE THE TARGET!\""
msgstr "\"你低估了……的力量——開玩笑的！消滅目標！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"There are no boulders punching or lasers dodging heroes to save you from "
"our forces! Or are there? We can kill them too!\""
msgstr "\"沒有能拳碎巨石或閃避激光的英雄來從我們手中拯救你！或許有？我們也能幹掉他們！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"So XEDRA truly did us a favor with their questionable ethics of "
"experiments, we've got no hostiles of government military forces that could "
"stop us now. There is still plenty of tension on the surface with these "
"monsters, but to deal with that we simply power up our guns. But your "
"faction of survivors is a meddling interloper in our matters, so we will "
"blast then simply throw to a pit all of YOU!\""
msgstr ""
"\"所以XEDRA那可疑的實驗倫理確實幫了我們大忙，現在已沒有政府軍敵對勢力能阻止我們。地表上這些怪物仍帶來不少緊張局勢，但對付它們我們只需給槍上膛。而你們這群倖存者派系卻來插手我們的事務，所以我們會先轟飛再把你們全部扔進坑裡！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"I have heard some rumors that these portals didn't do much of a favor to "
"our benefactors from the 'Alliance' in East Europe. They say that 'Alliance'"
" has encountered an enemy of the same strength as them there. They even have"
" a citadel there of some sorts! They use sandtraps, strange alien crabs. "
"Does not matter. Our combined forces will deal with them. We will also deal "
"not just with one anticitizen but with all of them including YOU!\""
msgstr ""
"\"我聽到些傳聞，說這些傳送門沒給我們在東歐的‘聯盟’贊助者帶來多少好處。據說‘聯盟’在那裡遭遇了與他們勢均力敵的敵人。他們甚至在那兒有某種要塞！他們使用沙坑陷阱、奇怪的外星螃蟹。無所謂。我們的聯合部隊會解決他們。我們不僅要解決一個反公民，還要解決所有反公民——包括你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Look at yourself! You are just as relentless as we are! You ram vehicles "
"into stores with locked doors, you burn down houses to kill a few pests, you"
" are the type of savages who bomb walls of buildings, with a horde of "
"monsters nearby, just to get your significant other a few snacks or a fancy "
"jewelry. We do that too, but we do that for a noble cause whereas you do "
"that for a cause of savagery!\""
msgstr ""
"\"看看你自己！你和我們一樣冷酷無情！你開車撞進鎖門的商店，燒燬房屋只為殺死幾隻害蟲，你是那種會在怪物群附近炸燬建築牆壁的野蠻人——就為了給你的另一半弄點零食或一件漂亮首飾。我們也這麼做，但我們是出於崇高事業，而你們卻是為了野蠻行徑！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"I don't trust these 'True Superiors' much, their boss is some genocidal "
"maniac obsessed with genetical perfection, but at least they help us kill "
"YOU!\""
msgstr "\"我不太信任這些‘真正上級’，他們的頭目是個痴迷基因完美的種族滅絕狂，但至少他們幫我們幹掉你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Join the military, they said. It will be fun to protect our Island, to "
"venture outside of our Island, they said. They didn't say that we would be "
"dealing with jacked up survivors that raid labs!\""
msgstr "\"他們說，加入軍隊吧。保衛我們的島嶼、探索島外會很有趣，他們說。可他們沒說我們要對付那些襲擊實驗室的強化倖存者！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"So first we had that lasers dodging fucker, then that fucking snake in a "
"red dress, now you? Do they train you? Is that why you all raid military "
"structures to turn your cars into moving homes with artillery weapons, have "
"both theoretical, practical knowledge of skills in majority of fields, wield"
" howitzers in your hands? Our Master is just trying to conquer the world!\""
msgstr ""
"\"先是那個閃激光的混蛋，然後是那個穿紅裙的臭蛇，現在是你？有人訓練你們嗎？所以你們才襲擊軍事設施，把車改成帶火炮的移動房屋，掌握多數領域的理論實踐知識，手裡拿著榴彈炮？我們的主人只是想征服世界！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"These Island soldiers have good training, but their Master is a science-"
"obsessed wannabe dictator who sees majority of others as potential servants,"
" not as a material to use to pave the road with, but at least they help us "
"kill YOU!\""
msgstr "\"這些島嶼士兵訓練有素，但他們的主人是個科學痴迷的獨裁妄想者，視多數人為潛在僕從——不是鋪路材料，但至少他們幫我們幹掉你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Why is our boss so obsessed with some boulder puncher? Hey, I saw you, "
"shoot the scum!\""
msgstr "\"為什麼我們老闆對某個拳碎巨石的傢伙這麼著迷？嘿，我看到你了，射殺那渣滓！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Our boss tells us fascinating stories about that boulder puncher's genes, "
"I wonder if he's out there somewhere?\""
msgstr "\"我們老闆常講那個拳碎巨石者基因的奇妙故事，我好奇他是不是還在某處活著？\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You survivors are a nuisance! How do you even struggle against us? Who's "
"behind that organization of wimps that makes these safety bases, shelters, "
"whatever? If that boulder puncher with his friends are still alive, then you"
" probably do have great chances against us. HEY, how dare you to make me "
"think like that? You're just a pest! I will kill YOU!\""
msgstr ""
"\"你們倖存者真是麻煩！你們怎麼還能抵抗我們？誰在背後組織那些建安全基地、避難所的懦夫？如果那個拳碎巨石者和他的朋友還活著，那你們或許真有機會對抗我們。嘿，你竟敢讓我這麼想？你只是個害蟲！我要殺了你！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"We think that this merchant works for these benevolent wimps. Our group is"
" trying to lure him into a trap but he does not fall for it. We keep on "
"sending these signals via his transmitters that he kindly scatters around "
"but he does not respond. Elusive pest!\""
msgstr "\"我們認為這商人替那些仁慈的懦夫工作。我們小組想引他入陷阱，但他不上當。我們不斷通過他好心散佈的發射器發送信號，但他不回應。狡猾的害蟲！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You, all of you, survivors, you decimate hordes of foul, interdimensional "
"creatures, stockpile so much ammo, raid military compounds to tune up your "
"cars with upgrades, raid labs to get mutagens, you can rebuild on an almost "
"industrial level! You could have joined us if you had not been so "
"stubborn!\""
msgstr ""
"\"你們，所有幸存者，你們殲滅成群的汙穢跨維度生物，囤積大量彈藥，襲擊軍事據點改裝車輛，突襲實驗室獲取突變劑，幾乎能在工業水平上重建！要不是這麼固執，你們本可以加入我們！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You really dare to challenge the ever-expanding unbreakable army built to "
"establish 'OUR' New World Order?\""
msgstr "\"你們竟敢挑戰為建立‘我們’新世界秩序而組建的、不斷擴張的無敵軍隊？\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. We would not just leave you here alone like that, "
"survivors! Remember, we are a team. We stick together! Let's show these "
"mooks how professional agents with survivors can fight against tyrants!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電通話。我們不會就這樣丟下你們孤軍奮戰，倖存者們！記住，我們是一個團隊。我們並肩作戰！讓這些打手看看，專業特工與倖存者如何對抗暴君！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. I have seen plenty of similar things in Europe, but "
"aliens? I doubt that they can play bingo. Different people, even different "
"species, but they all have the same obsession with power and domination!\""
msgstr "\"發起無線電通話。我在歐洲見過許多類似情況，但外星人？我懷疑他們會不會玩賓果遊戲。不同的人，甚至不同的物種，卻都對權力與統治有著同樣的痴迷！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Hey, a boulder puncher? How do they know? That blonde"
" pompous genocidal fucker must have gotten away! I knew that he would seize "
"the opportunity after XEDRA messed everything up everywhere!\""
msgstr "\"發起無線電通話。嘿，拳碎巨石者？他們怎麼知道的？那個金髮傲慢的種族滅絕混蛋肯定逃掉了！我就知道在XEDRA把一切搞砸後他會趁機行動！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. I still have no idea, how trader managed to get here."
" Do they have a guild of merchants of some sorts? I am glad to see him alive"
" obviously. Now, survivor, trust me, his stock saved me numerous amount of "
"times, I suggest you to put your distrust aside, because this man has proven"
" to be a friend of our organization so he is your friend too!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電通話。我還是不明白商人怎麼來到這裡的。他們有什麼商人公會嗎？看到他活著我當然高興。現在，倖存者，相信我，他的存貨救過我無數次，我建議你放下戒心，因為這人已證明是我們組織的朋友，所以他也是你的朋友！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. My engineer sister designed these boys, my military "
"partner lady equipped them with guns, my brother in law deploys them here "
"for his merchant friend to sell, whereas I? Of course, I have equipped them "
"with smashing devices for various smashing purposes that you have!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電通話。我工程師姐姐設計了這些小夥子，我軍方搭檔女士給他們配了槍，我姐夫為他的商人朋友部署他們到這裡銷售，而我呢？當然，我給他們裝備了各種粉碎裝置，以滿足你的各類粉碎需求！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. When I said that their plan sounded like aliens "
"invading Earth, I was joking back then. Little I knew that years after there"
" would be another wave of these madmen along with actual aliens invading "
"Earth, working with them! Oh, and look at the conditions, ravaged Earth, "
"huh? But there is still something to fight for, our along with your, "
"survivor, survival hopefully!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。當初我說他們的計劃聽起來像外星人入侵地球時，那只是玩笑話。我哪知道幾年後又會有一波這些瘋子，連同真正的外星人一起入侵地球，還跟他們合作！哦，看看這狀況，滿目瘡痍的地球，是吧？但我們仍有值得奮鬥的東西，我們——還有你，倖存者——希望能活下去！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Hey, don't be a wimp! Be a soldier! These boys are "
"merely support units, whereas it is directly your responsibility to lead us "
"to victory! What am I doing, you might ask? Well, you know that one can't "
"fight alone, right? I have my allies, my army of a family here, but we're "
"too far away from you and we can't spread out, that would be exactly what "
"these fuckers want us to do. Stick together! Get your friends, wife, "
"husband, partners, peers, children, arm yourself to fight against them! We "
"can do this, I know!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。嘿，別當懦夫！當個戰士！這些傢伙只是支援單位，而帶領我們走向勝利直接是你的責任！你可能會問我在做什麼？嗯，你知道一個人沒法單打獨鬥，對吧？我有我的盟友，我這裡的家族軍隊，但我們離你太遠，而且我們不能分散，那正是這些混蛋希望我們做的。團結起來！召集你的朋友、妻子、丈夫、夥伴、同輩、孩子，武裝自己對抗他們！我們能行，我知道！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. So you want to hear my advice? Be quick-witted, very "
"elusive, agile. Be on the run even when you fight. Use your strength with "
"your mind, with your intelligence. You know, unorthodox tactics, baiting, "
"evasive maneuvers, use these. That helped me greatly in Europe. I had "
"someone to learn from. Toxic, very untrustworthy person, but she was "
"cunning, hard to catch, a combat encounter for her was a mere dance "
"sometimes. Though, she was not a great person, I sometimes hope she would "
"get out of hiding to ally with us, but that simply reminds me of the reason "
"why her devious ways could not persuade me. Untrustworthy, unreliable. My "
"wife's brother gets especially mad when I mention her around him!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。所以你想聽我的建議？要機智，非常靈活，敏捷。即使在戰鬥時也要保持移動。用你的頭腦和智慧運用力量。你知道的，非常規戰術、誘敵、規避機動，用這些。這在歐洲幫了我大忙。我有個人可以學習。一個有毒、非常不可信的人，但她狡猾，難以捉摸，對她來說戰鬥有時只是一場舞蹈。不過，她不是個好人，我有時希望她能走出藏身之處與我們結盟，但這只是讓我想起為什麼她詭詐的方式無法說服我。不可信，不可靠。我提到她時，我妻子的兄弟特別生氣！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. You know, my veteran lady told me, concentrate on "
"survival, on rebuilding, there are no evil masterminds out there! Then I "
"showed her reports of our other agents. That's when she herself decided to "
"participate in construction of these boys. I am a soldier, I always remember"
" my duty, to kick asses of these fuckers! But, of course, we must survive, "
"rebuild, make communities, socialize, be these boring family people, now, "
"with my wife, with our family, I don't mind this boredom at all! You know, I"
" always have boulders and heads to punch!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。你知道，我的老兵女士告訴我，專注於生存和重建，外面沒有邪惡的主謀！然後我給她看了我們其他特工的報告。那時她自己決定參與建造這些傢伙。我是士兵，我始終記得我的職責，踢這些混蛋的屁股！但是，當然，我們必須生存、重建、建立社區、社交，成為這些無聊的家庭人士，現在，和我的妻子，和我們的家人在一起，我一點也不介意這種無聊！你知道，我總有巨石和腦袋可以揍！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Government used me with my engineer lady, threatened "
"us to do work for them. It was fun at first, but then I started to see who "
"they were. I got exhausted, paranoid. But she wanted to go deeper and "
"deeper, then this whole thing everywhere. I got tired of this so much, but "
"she sees her purpose in these things. I look at her, it changes my mind. I "
"could not even imagine that I would continue to fight against even tougher "
"creatures with her family on ravaged Earth, but I guess that she fuels this "
"fire in my soul, the fire of life!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。政府利用我和我的工程師女士，威脅我們為他們工作。起初很有趣，但後來我開始看清他們的真面目。我變得疲憊、多疑。但她想越陷越深，然後到處都是這種事。我厭倦透了，但她從這些事情中看到了自己的目標。我看著她，這改變了我的想法。我甚至無法想象我會繼續和她家人在滿目瘡痍的地球上對抗更強大的生物，但我想是她點燃了我靈魂中的火焰，生命的火焰！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Now why does this resemble a sci-fi movie conspiracy "
"of an even bigger magnitude than That City? Were these multiple walking "
"giant chasing weapons not enough? Of course not. Now we have aliens, fucking"
" XEDRA! Great, just great!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。現在為什麼這看起來像一部科幻電影陰謀，規模比那座城市還大？那些多個行走的巨型追擊武器還不夠嗎？當然不夠。現在我們有了外星人，該死的XEDRA！太好了，真是太好了！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. I prefer investigations along with more careful "
"approaches than this mess. The discoveries, the revealing of secrets of weak"
" wannabe dictators! The actions against them, legal, sometimes not so much. "
"But this? This is a mess, a horrible mess. XEDRA, prestigious team of "
"scientists, what have they done? I mean, at least I can use my skills as an "
"engineer to help all of us!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。比起這團糟，我更喜歡調查和更謹慎的方法。發現，揭示那些軟弱想當獨裁者的秘密！針對他們的行動，合法的，有時不那麼合法。但這個？這是一團糟，可怕的混亂。XEDRA，聲名顯赫的科學家團隊，他們做了什麼？我是說，至少我可以用我的工程技能幫助我們所有人！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Just how do they even know about us? These evil "
"mooks. Not all of them seem like mooks, these are a different kind. They "
"seem to be supported by someone grand, devious, pragmatic, not sure. If it's"
" this blonde fucking maniac, how did he team up with aliens? Oh, of course, "
"'The Perfect Genes' obsession with his strength of a beast. Must have "
"convinced them that he knows better. Must have threatened them to dance to "
"his tune too!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。他們到底怎麼知道我們的？這些邪惡的嘍囉。不是所有都像嘍囉，這些是另一種。他們似乎被某個偉大、狡詐、務實的人支持，不確定。如果是那個金髮混蛋瘋子，他怎麼和外星人組隊的？哦，當然，'完美基因'對他野獸般力量的痴迷。一定說服了他們他更懂。一定也威脅他們按他的調子跳舞！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. We have always fought these things, not thinking of "
"using them as tools. We fight it's weaponized version too now, but as other "
"researchers have proven, this one is benevolent at it's core. Some doubt it,"
" but there is progress, there are good results, between The Blob infested "
"water along with this the choice is obvious. It can be used to produce "
"healthy drugs, cure, protection against other mutations. It's a great tool, "
"but as any tool, it can be weaponized, used with other purposes. That's who "
"we fight against of course!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。我們一直與這些東西戰鬥，沒想過把它們當工具用。我們現在也對抗它的武器化版本，但正如其他研究者證明的，這個本質上是良性的。有人懷疑，但有進展，有好結果，在Blob感染的水和這個之間，選擇很明顯。它可以用來生產健康藥物、治療、對抗其他突變。這是個偉大的工具，但像任何工具一樣，它可以被武器化，用於其他目的。那當然是我們對抗的對象！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. I wanted to concentrate on rebuilding, on living as a"
" boring family, doing boring things, trying to help local survivors, trying "
"to form communities. There is plenty of madness outside already, I don't "
"enjoy any of this because this was always my dangerous work. It's my wish to"
" build a safe world for me with my family basically that always gave me this"
" enthusiasm, this zeal! Now, though, thanks to my family, thanks to my other"
" beneficial skills that I have learned, thanks to you, survivors, I can "
"allow myself to do more work in the background. I can teach a new generation"
" of fighters like me!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。我曾想專注於重建，過無聊的家庭生活，做無聊的事，試圖幫助當地倖存者，試圖建立社區。外面已經有足夠的瘋狂，我不享受任何這些，因為這一直是我危險的工作。基本上，為我和我的家人建立一個安全世界的願望，總是給我這種熱情，這種熱忱！現在，多虧了我的家人，多虧了我學到的其他有益技能，多虧了你們，倖存者，我可以允許自己在幕後做更多工作。我可以教導新一代像我一樣的戰士！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. It would be so interesting to investigate the rumors "
"about East Europe with regards to these other aliens there! It sounds like "
"an alien militia of a similar force to the force of the ones here but they "
"are enemies! Well, I have designed some of these robots based on rumors of "
"usefulness of small flying drones they use, but instead of slash attacks, "
"it's capable of stunning along with ranged attacks. Still, hacks enemies "
"pretty greatly, so it's a manhack obviously. Whereas UGVs were easier to "
"create, using local machines as the base, though, these ground units, they "
"require more scrap to craft than air units, obviously! Since when do I use "
"my brother's military language? Interesting!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。調查關於東歐那些其他外星人的謠言會多麼有趣！聽起來像一支外星民兵，力量與這裡的相似，但他們是敵人！嗯，我設計了一些這些機器人，基於他們使用的小型飛行無人機有用的謠言，但不是劈砍攻擊，它能眩暈和遠程攻擊。仍然，能很好地黑入敵人，所以它顯然是個人類黑客。而UGV更容易製造，使用本地機器作為基礎，不過，這些地面單位，它們需要比空中單位更多的廢料來製作，顯然！我什麼時候開始用我兄弟的軍事語言了？有趣！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Look, if you want to be able to go to lengths I go "
"to, which is technically important, considering all of this mess around, you"
" need to be universal. Be able to run, dodge, block, parry, counter, fight, "
"craft, construct, learn, you know. Not everything of this is mandatory, "
"depending on your other skills, on your allies, but to always learn is "
"mandatory. The greatest skill that can be ever learned is to learn how to "
"learn. This skill will always feed you, when there seems to be no food "
"around. This will let you find great ways to get out of a lot of situations "
"alive which is proven by thousands of years of humanity's experience!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。聽著，如果你想達到我達到的程度，這在技術上很重要，考慮到周圍所有這些混亂，你需要全面。能夠跑、躲閃、格擋、招架、反擊、戰鬥、製作、建造、學習，你知道。不是所有這些都強制，取決於你的其他技能、你的盟友，但始終學習是強制的。能學到的最偉大技能是學習如何學習。當週圍似乎沒有食物時，這個技能總會養活你。這將讓你找到許多方法活著擺脫很多情況，這是人類幾千年經驗證明的！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. What can an engineer who is greatly curious by nature"
" suggest? Science! Engineering! But you should not be alone. Not only "
"science needs these who are capable of thinking, capable of being curious, "
"to flourish, but also it needs these in high quantities. You need allies. To"
" manufacture, technically, a few scientists, but even they can be from "
"different fields, can suffice, to make an industry you need at least dozens "
"of scientists. But the most important thing is to believe in something, "
"believe in someone too. To devote your energy, your work, your efforts for "
"the sake of something truly great!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。一個天生非常好奇的工程師能建議什麼？科學！工程！但你不應該孤單。不僅科學需要那些能夠思考、能夠好奇的人來繁榮，而且需要大量這樣的人。你需要盟友。技術上，製造，幾個科學家，但即使他們可以來自不同領域，可能足夠，要建立一個產業，你至少需要幾十個科學家。但最重要的是相信某事，也相信某人。為了真正偉大的東西，奉獻你的能量、你的工作、你的努力！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. Seeing me become more paranoid, violent, seeing "
"wearying of my soul, because of constant battles against these creatures, "
"now these fuckers too, my sweetie suggested me to become a leader of a "
"community in a local region. That's what I always wanted. I can only pray "
"that there will be times of love with peace in our lands with us, with you, "
"survivor, alive, I hope! Times when we will be able to learn skills for our "
"leisure, times when we will have more leisure, means to relax, not just to "
"reduce stress of horrors witnessed outside. Now, I will concentrate on "
"teaching survivors around me all that I know along with keeping my family "
"safe! Though, I dream of love with peace, I will always remain a fighter, I "
"know that for sure!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。看到我因為不斷對抗這些生物，現在還有這些混蛋，變得更偏執、暴力，看到我靈魂疲憊，我的甜心建議我成為當地一個社區的領袖。那是我一直想要的。我只能祈禱，在我們土地上，和我們，和你，倖存者，活著，我希望，會有愛與和平的時光！那時我們將能為閒暇學習技能，那時我們將有更多閒暇，放鬆的方式，而不僅僅是為了減輕外面目睹的恐怖壓力。現在，我將專注於教導我周圍的倖存者我所知道的一切，同時保護我的家人安全！雖然，我夢想著愛與和平，我將永遠是個戰士，我確信！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. It was always hard for me to understand motives of my"
" love when he said that he was distrustful of our government, that we were "
"dealing with their former allies that turned on them. That I didn't want to "
"consider the bigger picture of our missions. That these dictators were "
"always tied to organizations like XEDRA but made look like they were not. I "
"realized that much later, but he didn't give up on me! Though, I was too "
"focused on trying to do good, not thinking for a second, which led us "
"partially to this, he still supports my work now! That's true, he always "
"pushes me to see the truth myself, not forcing me, but I thought that he "
"pursued his own interests. I love him so much along with my brother with my "
"sister in law who are always looking after us!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。當我的愛人說他不信任我們的政府，說我們在處理他們以前的盟友，那些背叛了他們的人時，我總是很難理解他的動機。說我不想考慮我們任務的更大圖景。說這些獨裁者總是與像XEDRA這樣的組織有聯繫，但看起來好像沒有。我後來才意識到很多，但他沒有放棄我！雖然，我太專注於試圖做好事，一秒鐘都沒想，這讓我們部分地走到了這一步，他現在仍然支持我的工作！真的，他總是推動我自己看到真相，不強迫我，但我以為他追求自己的利益。我非常愛他，還有我的兄弟和嫂子，他們總是照顧我們！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Initiate Radio Call. What frequency is this? Stranger, is that you? Excuse"
" me, I am testing my transmitter! Do you like these robots? I hope you do! "
"If you wonder, who are these people that connect to this frequency on the "
"radio devices of your robots. Well, it's the GREATEST of the GREATEST of "
"benevolent agents, stranger. I know them for a long time thanks to my "
"sources. That's so impolite of me to distract you! I got to go do my work. "
"Let's hope that no one else traced this frequency, stranger!\""
msgstr ""
"\"發起無線電呼叫。這是什麼頻率？陌生人，是你嗎？抱歉，我在測試我的發射器！你喜歡這些機器人嗎？我希望你喜歡！如果你想知道，這些連接到你的機器人無線電設備上這個頻率的人是誰。嗯，是最偉大的最偉大的仁慈特工，陌生人。多虧我的消息來源，我認識他們很久了。我這樣打擾你真是不禮貌！我得去做我的工作了。希望沒有其他人追蹤到這個頻率，陌生人！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You've made a foolish choice siding with these wimps. With our combined "
"forces - you and 'US' - 'WE' could have asserted our dominance over the "
"ENTIRE world!\""
msgstr "\"你做了個愚蠢的選擇，站在這些懦夫一邊。以我們聯合的力量——你和'我們'——'我們'本可以宣稱對整個世界的統治！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Can you even imagine what powers 'WE' have managed to acquire? With them, "
"we can put what remains of this world to it's knees and fully subjugate it "
"all!\""
msgstr "\"你能想象'我們'獲得了什麼力量嗎？有了它們，我們可以讓這個世界剩下的部分跪倒，完全征服一切！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You've seen almost everything what our Island has to offer and you still "
"do not realize what 'WE' are TRULY capable of?\""
msgstr "\"你幾乎看到了我們島嶼提供的一切，你仍然沒有意識到'我們'真正能做到什麼？\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You could have been someone. Your skills and knowledge - everything gone "
"to waste because of your silly principles!\""
msgstr "\"你本可以成為一個人物。你的技能和知識——一切都因為你可笑的原則浪費了！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Witness the POWER!\""
msgstr "\"見證這力量！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"Prepare for your destruction!\""
msgstr "\"準備迎接你的毀滅！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"'Madman'? I only crave to change this world for the better, but the "
"remaining humans MUST bind with this POWER, the worthy will live and serve "
"'US'. The unworthy will die and be gotten rid of like useless chaff!\""
msgstr "\"'瘋子'？我只渴望讓這個世界變得更好，但剩下的人類必須與這力量結合，有價值者將活著並服務'我們'。無價值者將死去，像無用的糠秕一樣被清除！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"We finally meet. EVERYTHING that I'VE WORKED SO DILIGENTLY ON, BUILT, "
"CREATED and you've destroyed, killed, eradicated... you shall pay for "
"EVERYTHING dearly! Then the NEW ERA will begin!\""
msgstr "\"我們終於見面了。我如此勤奮工作、建造、創造的一切，而你摧毀、殺死、根除了……你將為一切付出沉重代價！然後新時代將開始！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You've lost your only chance to redeem yourself - you could just unite "
"with 'US', with ME, to found a new Earth built upon the flesh and bones of "
"the unworthy and filthy ones!\""
msgstr "\"你失去了救贖的唯一機會——你本可以加入'我們'，加入我，建立一個建立在無價值和骯髒者的血肉和骨頭上的新地球！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"'Nevulion'? The prophecy? Hah, the occult mumbo-jumbo. I made it up with "
"my propaganda. Yet, they were right about EVERYTHING - I AM THE NEVULION, I "
"AM THE PROPHECY and I SHALL DESTROY YOU, FEEBLE HUMAN!\""
msgstr ""
"\"'Nevulion'？預言？哈，神秘的胡言亂語。我用我的宣傳編造的。然而，他們關於一切都說對了——我就是NEVULION，我就是預言，我將摧毀你，軟弱的人類！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You strive to destroy modified versions of this organism that I have "
"modified, even though in it's initial state it was almost useless, and "
"anything associated with it as if it's some kind of a corruption. Oh, but I "
"am FAR from being corrupted - I've awoken from the deepest slumber - the "
"slumber of ignorance!\""
msgstr ""
"\"你努力摧毀我修改過的這種生物體的修改版本，儘管在初始狀態下它幾乎無用，以及與它相關的任何東西，好像它是某種腐化。哦，但我遠未被腐化——我從最深的沉睡中醒來——無知的沉睡！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid "\"How are you still alive? Die already, you feeble puny being!\""
msgstr "\"你怎麼還活著？快死吧，你這軟弱渺小的生物！\""

#: .\Monsters\mon_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You have killed all of my closest and most trusted people. Even though "
"they clearly gave you MULTIPLE chances to RECONSIDER your decision, to "
"acquire the power and join us! Yet, you acted like a vile and inhumane guest"
" - slaughtered them - chomped the hands that wanted to feed YOU!\""
msgstr ""
"\"你殺了我所有最親近和最信任的人。儘管他們顯然給了你多次機會重新考慮你的決定，獲得力量並加入我們！然而，你表現得像個邪惡和不人道的客人——屠殺了他們——咬了想餵你的手！\""

