msgid ""
"Made by a secret benevolent organization to fight against tyrants with alien"
" invaders. BL9 symbiote, somehow, taught to control manhacks, forming unique"
" abilities, ranging from distracting to smashing, shooting it's organic gun "
"that can stun. The ones that are sold by Strange Trader are always friendly "
"because of their purchaser's direct control. The ones that are found in the "
"wild that are not controlled, however, because of greater conditions of "
"symbiosis of BL9 with living creatures compared to robots, can attack every "
"creature around them indiscriminately. If you don't control it, proceed with"
" caution hopefully"
msgstr ""
"由一個秘密的仁慈組織製造，用於對抗暴君與外星入侵者。BL9共生體不知何故學會了控制追獵者，形成了獨特能力，從干擾到粉碎，並射擊其能擊暈的有機槍械。由奇異商人出售的個體因購買者的直接控制而始終友好。然而，在野外發現的未受控制個體，由於BL9與生物共生的條件優於機器人，可能無差別攻擊周圍所有生物。若你不控制它，請務必謹慎行事。"

