#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armed BL9-Cultist - Flail'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"A zealot infused with the BL9. It appears to be sentient, having all "
"characteristics of a normal person except for strangely solemn gaze, "
"disturbingly pale skin and bloodshot eyes indicating the presence of "
"artificially modified BL9 to make them more violent, obedient,  their motive"
" is to kill those that didn't accept the blessing of their \"dios\", this "
"one is armed with a flail and it seems to know how to use it well."
msgstr ""
"一個注入了BL9的狂熱者。它似乎具有感知能力，擁有正常人的所有特徵，除了異常肅穆的目光、令人不安的蒼白皮膚和佈滿血絲的眼睛，這表明存在經過人工改造的BL9，使其更具攻擊性和服從性，其動機是殺死那些不接受其“神”祝福的人。這一個手持連枷，並且似乎很擅長使用它。"

