"bloodshot eyes indicating the presence of artificially modified BL9 to make "
"them more violent, obedient,  they will do their best to stop any intruder "
"that managed to infiltrate their compound, this one is armed with a rifle "
"and it obviously knows how to use it well."
msgstr ""
