#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\mon_placeholders.json
msgid "rust fist brute"
msgid_plural "rust fist brutes"
msgstr[0] "鏽拳蠻兵"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Dr.Gonzalez"
msgid_plural "Dr.Gonzalezs"
msgstr[0] "岡薩雷斯博士"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dr.Gonzalez'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A tall male figure in tattered blooded, mudded clothes of a rural farmer "
"wearing a burlap sack over his head with two holes in it in the place of "
"eyes, his gaping wide eyes filled with anger and malice can be seen even "
"from long distance, whirring of his chainsaw can be evidently heard, the "
"sound of it sends chills down your spine"
msgstr ""
"一個高大的男性身影，身著沾滿血跡和泥汙的鄉村農民破舊衣物，頭上套著一個麻袋，麻袋眼部位置有兩個洞，他那充滿憤怒與惡意的瞪大雙眼即使在遠處也能看見，其鏈鋸的轟鳴聲清晰可聞，那聲音讓你脊背發涼"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "BL9 Giant"
msgid_plural "BL9 Giants"
msgstr[0] "BL9巨人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Giant'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A result of one of many horrible inhumane and vile experiments conducted by "
"'THEM' - 23 feet tall giant buff humanoid that has basically lost all of "
"it's intelligence and was so unsafe and violent that the cult had to isolate"
" them and keep them locked up in some distant inaccessible areas in giant "
"cages"
msgstr ""
"這是'他們'進行的眾多可怕、不人道且邪惡的實驗之一的結果——一個23英尺高、肌肉發達的人形巨人，基本上已喪失所有智力，且如此危險和暴力，以至於邪教不得不將其隔離，並鎖在遙遠難及之處的巨大籠子裡。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'BL9 Giant'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s is going wild at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s正在%3$s發狂！</color>"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Blind Clawer"
msgid_plural "Blind Clawers"
msgstr[0] "盲爪怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blind Clawer'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Tall augmented human host of the BL9, they call it 'The Clawer' due to it "
"being armed with razor sharp mechanical claws that it's capable of "
"activating at will, in order to constrain indiscriminate killing power, it's"
" eyelids were stitched together, though, BL9 has still managed to retain "
"some of their sight making them not fully blind"
msgstr ""
"一個高大的、經過強化的BL9人類宿主，因其裝備有鋒利的機械爪並能隨意激活，被稱為'爪怪'。為了限制其無差別的殺戮能力，它的眼皮被縫合在一起，然而，BL9仍設法保留了一些視力，使其並非完全失明。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'Blind Clawer'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s charges at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s向%3$s發起衝鋒！</color>"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Assassin"
msgid_plural "The Assassins"
msgstr[0] "刺客"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Assassin'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A reptile-like mutant with highly resistant scales and a long, double-edged "
"tail. Aside from it's nimble and deadly assaults, it can also blend with the"
" surroundings, if conditions are met."
msgstr "一種類似爬行動物的突變體，擁有高抗性的鱗片和一條長而雙刃的尾巴。除了敏捷致命的攻擊外，在條件滿足時，它還能融入周圍環境。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Twisted One"
msgid_plural "The Twisted Ones"
msgstr[0] "扭曲者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Twisted One'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Mutated human cocoon which acts as a head of a terrible tentacle "
"amalgamation foundation and body of which is formed by the heavily mutated "
"remains of The Assassin with multiple stretching gaping mouths lined with "
"dozens of razor sharp teeth, tentacles of unknown origin emerge from it's "
"back acting like the legs of it which may as well attack from a long "
"distance"
msgstr ""
"一個突變的人類繭，充當著一個可怕觸手融合體的頭部，其身體由嚴重突變的'刺客'殘骸構成，上面有多張伸展的、佈滿數十顆鋒利牙齒的大嘴，未知來源的觸手從其背部伸出，充當其腿部，並能從遠距離發起攻擊。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'The Twisted One'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'The Chimera'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s sends a tentacle towards %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s向%3$s甩出一條觸手！</color>"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Inhravtidius Super Soldier"
msgid_plural "Inhravtidius Super Soldiers"
msgstr[0] "因赫拉維迪烏斯超級士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Inhravtidius Super Soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Inhravtidius Mutant Amalgamation with all of it's typical traits: thick "
"armor-like carapace on it's torso, 2 spiked antennas, protruding from it's "
"strangely shaped head, countless amount of eyes, 2 spiked tentacles, "
"emerging from sides of this creature, 4 medium-sized crustacean legs, 2 "
"pincers in the place of it's arms. What distinguishes this creature from "
"other Amalgamations is that it is bigger, faster, seems to be trained as an "
"experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking gun in one of it's "
"pincers"
msgstr ""
"因赫拉維迪烏斯突變融合體，具備其所有典型特徵：軀幹覆蓋著厚重的甲殼狀外骨骼，兩根帶刺的觸角從其形狀奇特的頭部突出，無數隻眼睛，兩根帶刺的觸手從該生物兩側伸出，四條中等大小的甲殼類腿部，雙臂位置是兩隻鉗子。此生物與其他融合體的區別在於它更大、更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它的一隻鉗子握著一把外觀奇特的有機質感的槍。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Super Soldier fires it's organic blaster!"
msgstr "超級士兵發射了它的有機衝擊槍！"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Yengnutrium Super Soldier"
msgid_plural "Yengnutrium Super Soldiers"
msgstr[0] "延格努特里姆超級士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Yengnutrium Super Soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Yengnutrium Mutant Amalgamation with all of it's typical traits: 2 "
"asymetrically growing heads - one resembles a mix of a mantis' and fly's "
"head with multiple rapidly blinking eyes - the other resembles a mix of a "
"locust's and cockroach's head with 2 eyes at both sides of it. What's left "
"of it's humanoid body is barely recognizable - it's vertically elongated "
"with 2 winged tentacles protruding from it's back. 2 serrated curved claws "
"in the place of the arms, and 2 spiked far apart insect legs. What "
"distinguishes this creature from other Amalgamations is that it is bigger, "
"faster, seems to be trained as an experimental soldier. It holds a strange "
"organic-looking gun in one of it's claws"
msgstr ""
"Yengnutrium突變融合體，具備其所有典型特徵：兩個不對稱生長的頭部——一個類似螳螂與蒼蠅頭部的混合體，長有多隻快速眨動的眼睛；另一個類似蝗蟲與蟑螂頭部的混合體，兩側各有一隻眼睛。其殘留的人形軀幹幾乎無法辨認——縱向拉長，背部伸出兩條帶翼觸手。雙臂位置是兩把鋸齒狀彎曲利爪，兩條帶刺的昆蟲腿分得很開。此生物與其他融合體的區別在於它體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一隻爪子握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Ulniviunite Super Soldier"
msgid_plural "Ulniviunite Super Soldiers"
msgstr[0] "Ulniviunite超級士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ulniviunite Super Soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Ulniviunite Mutant Amalgamation with all of it's typical traits: it's body "
"is entirely covered with mucousy thick and durable scales, it's head is "
"shrinked - it's mouth has turned into a lamprey-type one with forked-tongue-"
"like 2 long spiked tentacles hanging from it, grotesquely fleshy set of "
"spiked tentacles emerge from 3 sides of it's back, it's hands have turned "
"into incredibly sharp and sturdy claws. What distinguishes this creature "
"from other Amalgamations is that it is bigger, faster, seems to be trained "
"as an experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking gun in one of"
" it's claws"
msgstr ""
"Ulniviunite突變融合體，具備其所有典型特徵：全身覆蓋著粘稠厚實且耐用的鱗片，頭部萎縮——嘴部變成七鰓鰻型結構，懸掛著兩條分叉舌狀的長刺觸手，背部三側冒出"
" grotesquely "
"肉質帶刺觸手叢，雙手變成異常鋒利堅固的利爪。此生物與其他融合體的區別在於它體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一隻爪子握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Ezrondium Super Soldier"
msgid_plural "Ezrondium Super Soldiers"
msgstr[0] "Ezrondium超級士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ezrondium Super Soldier'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Ezrondium Mutant Amalgamation with all of it's typical traits: it's head is "
"elongated with countless glittering ruby red eyes, the torso - covered with "
"great amount of red hair and filled with fleshy holes from which protrude "
"multiple tentacles, swinging wildly in all directions, lower part - of a "
"bloody red colored enormous arachnid. What distinguishes this creature from "
"other Amalgamations is that it is bigger, faster, seems to be trained as an "
"experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking gun in one of it's "
"tentacles"
msgstr ""
"Ezrondium突變融合體，具備其所有典型特徵：頭部拉長，長有無數閃爍的寶石紅眼睛；軀幹覆蓋大量紅毛，佈滿肉質孔洞，從中伸出多根觸手向四面八方狂亂揮舞；下半身是血紅色的巨型蛛形綱結構。此生物與其他融合體的區別在於它體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一根觸手握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Weapon of Evolution - Type 1"
msgid_plural "Weapon of Evolution - Type 1s"
msgstr[0] "進化兵器 - 1型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Weapon of Evolution - Type 1'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Humanoid brute amalgamation of all feral aliens, that were brought to Earth "
"essentially by 'Alliance' for them to experiment on. Inhravtidius carapace "
"on it's torso along with a pincer in the place of it's left arm. Yengnutrium"
" wings, protruding from it's back along with a razor sharp serrated claw in "
"the place of it's right arm. Ulniviunite slime on it's torso along with a "
"lamprey-type mouth from which a long, whip-like spiked tongue is stretching."
" Ezrondium arachnid legs, incredibly sharp, piercing floor as it moves. "
"Tentacles, emerging from various parts of it's body essentially. Unlike "
"other beasts, this one is in particular rage, as if it was made for hunting."
" It is bigger, faster compared to other beasts, seems to be trained as an "
"experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking gun in one of it's "
"tentacles"
msgstr ""
"所有人形外星野獸的融合體，本質上由'聯盟'帶到地球進行實驗。軀幹覆蓋Inhravtidius甲殼，左臂位置為鉗肢。背部伸出Yengnutrium翅膀，右臂位置為剃刀般鋒利的鋸齒爪。軀幹附著Ulniviunite粘液，七鰓鰻型嘴中伸出長鞭狀帶刺舌頭。Ezrondium蛛形腿異常鋒利，移動時刺穿地面。身體各處均伸出觸手。與其他野獸不同，這隻尤其狂暴，彷彿專為狩獵而生。相比其他野獸體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一根觸手握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "BL9 Regenerator"
msgid_plural "BL9 Regenerators"
msgstr[0] "BL9再生者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Regenerator'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
" An experimental pale mutant with skinny limbs and dreadful visage. It's "
"strong regenerative prowess is an offset to it's fragile body."
msgstr "實驗性蒼白突變體，四肢纖細，面容可怖。其強大的再生能力彌補了脆弱身體的缺陷。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "BL9 Iron Maiden"
msgid_plural "BL9 Iron Maidens"
msgstr[0] "BL9鐵處女"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Iron Maiden'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"An experimental mutant with several spikes emerging from it's body. Similar "
"to regenerator, but it seems to take full control of it's protrusions."
msgstr "實驗性突變體，身體多處伸出尖刺。與再生者類似，但似乎能完全控制其突起物。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Chimera"
msgid_plural "The Chimeras"
msgstr[0] "奇美拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Chimera'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A horrifying chimera of human, insect, and reptile DNA fused imperfectly "
"into a single being, itself hosting the BL9.It has the upper part of a human"
" torso and a human head, it's visage is monstrously warped and marked by "
"strange scars upon it's nape and crown, a clawed arm, and a tentacle in "
"place of the other one"
msgstr ""
"人類、昆蟲與爬行動物DNA不完美融合而成的恐怖奇美拉，其自身寄宿著BL9。擁有人類軀幹上半部與人類頭部，面容 monstrously "
"扭曲，後頸與頭頂留有詭異疤痕，一隻手臂為利爪，另一隻手臂位置為觸手"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Mutated Chimera"
msgid_plural "The Mutated Chimeras"
msgstr[0] "突變奇美拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Mutated Chimera'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A horrifying chimera of human, insect, and reptile DNA fused imperfectly "
"into a single being, itself hosting the BL9, it has mutated since it's first"
" stages and now has a tentacle sprouting from it's back ending in a gaping "
"mouth, lined with dozens of teeth. This tentacle also sports a heavy pair of"
" pincers"
msgstr ""
"人類、昆蟲與爬行動物DNA不完美融合而成的恐怖奇美拉，其自身寄宿著BL9，自初期階段已發生突變，現背部伸出一根觸手，末端為佈滿數十顆牙齒的裂口。此觸手還帶有一對重型鉗肢"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'The Mutated Chimera'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s slashes %3$s with it's pincer!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s用鉗肢劈砍%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Mutated Elite General"
msgid_plural "Mutated Elite Generals"
msgstr[0] "突變精英將軍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mutated Elite General'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"A tall buffed up human wearing a face camouflage and a light armor, it looks"
" like an absolutely normal human compared to everything that you had to face"
" so far, except for the fact that it seems to have inhumane agility and "
"reflexes, moreover it's most prominent feature is the huge blade-shield-like"
" BL9 growth that has taken over it's right arm entirely"
msgstr ""
"高大魁梧的人類，佩戴面部迷彩與輕甲，與你迄今為止面對的一切相比看似完全正常，除了其似乎具備非人的敏捷性與反射神經，此外最顯著的特徵是巨大的刀盾狀BL9增生組織完全取代了其右臂"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'Mutated Elite General'}"'s spell
#. "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s leaps at %3$s!</color> and slashes wildly"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s撲向%3$s！</color>並瘋狂劈砍"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "The Vile One"
msgid_plural "The Vile Ones"
msgstr[0] "穢惡者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Vile One'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Severely mutated astoundingly large, multi-legged beast. The crustacean-"
"styled legs are all still connected to what seems to be a humanoid body, "
"which hangs from his mutant form like a vestigial limb. His head is now "
"attached to a long serpentine neck and is surrounded by hard, blade-like "
"mandibles. A series of eyes are also dotted around the body, one on each "
"joint of the legs and another large eye in it's mouth"
msgstr ""
"嚴重突變的驚人巨型多足野獸。甲殼綱風格的腿足仍全部連接在看似人形的軀幹上，該軀幹像退化肢體般懸掛在其突變體形態下方。頭部現附著於長蛇狀頸部，周圍環繞著堅硬的刀刃狀顎肢。身體各處亦散佈著眼睛，每條腿關節各有一隻，口中另有一隻巨眼"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'The Vile One'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s's head stretches then crunches at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s的頭部伸長然後猛咬%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Weapon of Evolution - Type 2"
msgid_plural "Weapon of Evolution - Type 2s"
msgstr[0] "進化兵器 - 2型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Weapon of Evolution - Type 2'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Humanoid giant amalgamation of all feral aliens, that were brought to Earth "
"essentially by 'Alliance' for them to experiment on. Inhravtidius carapace "
"on it's torso along with a pincer in the place of it's left arm. Yengnutrium"
" wings, protruding from it's back along with a razor sharp serrated claw in "
"the place of it's right arm. Ulniviunite slime on it's torso along with a "
"lamprey-type mouth from which a long, whip-like spiked tongue is stretching."
" Ezrondium arachnid legs, incredibly sharp, piercing floor as it moves. "
"Tentacles, emerging from various parts of it's body essentially. Unlike "
"other beasts, this one is in particular rage, as if it was made for hunting."
" It is bigger, faster compared to other beasts, seems to be trained as an "
"experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking gun in one of it's "
"tentacles"
msgstr ""
"所有人形外星野獸的巨型融合體，本質上由'聯盟'帶到地球進行實驗。軀幹覆蓋Inhravtidius甲殼，左臂位置為鉗肢。背部伸出Yengnutrium翅膀，右臂位置為剃刀般鋒利的鋸齒爪。軀幹附著Ulniviunite粘液，七鰓鰻型嘴中伸出長鞭狀帶刺舌頭。Ezrondium蛛形腿異常鋒利，移動時刺穿地面。身體各處均伸出觸手。與其他野獸不同，這隻尤其狂暴，彷彿專為狩獵而生。相比其他野獸體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一根觸手握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid "Weapon of Evolution - Type 3"
msgid_plural "Weapon of Evolution - Type 3s"
msgstr[0] "進化兵器 - 3型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Weapon of Evolution - Type 3'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\pecurial_bastards.json
msgid ""
"Humanoid giant grotesque amalgamation of all feral aliens, that were brought"
" to Earth essentially by 'Alliance' for them to experiment on. Inhravtidius "
"carapace on it's torso along with a pincer in the place of it's left arm. "
"Yengnutrium wings, protruding from it's back along with a razor sharp "
"serrated claw in the place of it's right arm. Ulniviunite slime on it's "
"torso along with a lamprey-type mouth from which a long, whip-like spiked "
"tongue is stretching. Ezrondium arachnid legs, incredibly sharp, piercing "
"floor as it moves. Tentacles, emerging from various parts of it's body "
"essentially. Unlike other beasts, this one is in particular rage, as if it "
"was made for hunting. It is bigger, faster compared to other beasts, seems "
"to be trained as an experimental soldier. It holds a strange organic-looking"
" gun in one of it's tentacles"
msgstr ""
"所有人形外星野獸的巨型 grotesque "
"融合體，本質上由'聯盟'帶到地球進行實驗。軀幹覆蓋Inhravtidius甲殼，左臂位置為鉗肢。背部伸出Yengnutrium翅膀，右臂位置為剃刀般鋒利的鋸齒爪。軀幹附著Ulniviunite粘液，七鰓鰻型嘴中伸出長鞭狀帶刺舌頭。Ezrondium蛛形腿異常鋒利，移動時刺穿地面。身體各處均伸出觸手。與其他野獸不同，這隻尤其狂暴，彷彿專為狩獵而生。相比其他野獸體型更大、速度更快，似乎被訓練為實驗性士兵。它用一根觸手握著一把外形奇特的有機質槍械"

